      #### Adam Darowski ####

      Ever since introducing the [Hall of wWAR](http://darowski.com/hall-of-wwar) in March of 2011, Adam Darowski has been obsessed with the idea of the Hall of Stats. A web designer and developer by day for [PatientsLikeMe](http://patientslikeme.com), he researches, writes, designs, and codes about baseball in his spare time (and for such sites as [High Heat Stats](http://www.highheatstats.com/author/adam/) and [Beyond the Box Score](http://www.sbnation.com/users/adarowski/blog). Adam tweets about baseball at [@baseballtwit](http://twitter.com/baseballtwit) and everything else at [@adarowski](http://twitter.com/adarowski).

