      A former co-worker of Adam’s at PatientsLikeMe, Jeffrey is currently a Rails developer for [Terrible Labs](http://terriblelabs.com). Adam and Jeffrey previously collaborated on the [Red Sox Hall of wWAR](http://redsox.hallofstats.com/), a [Baseball Hack Day](http://baseballhackday.com/) project. Jeffrey is simply the Babe Ruth of Rails developers. There is nobody better. You can follow Jeffrey on Twitter at [@semanticart](http://twitter.com/semanticart).

